snippet.title: Skye: The Misty Isle - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a journey through a hyper-realistic, Viking survival game, set on the Isle of Skye.
Sharpen your axe and prepare to sail - Valhalla awaits! 🪓

🌐 Website: https://auroragamestudios.co.uk
🎮 Steam: https://bit.ly/SkyeSteam
💬 Discord: https://discord.gg/skye-themistyisle
🔗 LinkTree: https://linktr.ee/AuroraGameStudios

🎵 Music by @AnTuagh
